Title: Maxcare Virgin Coconut (Cold Pressed) Hair Oil(250 ml)
Description: Virgin Coconut Oil(VCO), is also called ?White Coconut Oil?. It is extracted from freshly shredded and first-pressed coconut meat of choice and mature coconuts.It was termed Virgin because it is pure as in white, it does not undergo any hydro-generation or any heating process, it is unrefined, unbleached and has not under gone any deodorizing process. Unlike other coconut oil that is extracted through heat, VCO does not possess that latik odor, but fresh aroma of coconut oil.VCO is the most healthy and versatile of all vegetable oils. It is composed primarily of medium chain fatty acids(MCFA) or Triglycerides. MCFA are quickly digested and it?s transformed immediately by the body as energy. This also means that VCO does not produce fat and cholesterol. Saturated fats found in VCO are actually good and promotes health.VCO has anti-microbial properties. Its high Lauric acid content makes it a natural anti-bacterial, antiviral and anti-fungal substance. It is also found to be very stable so it does not oxidize easily. As a result, Vitamins A, C and E, which strengthen the body?s immune system are not depleted. Vitamin E in the oil also helps make the hair and skin smooth.Lauric acid(fat called monolaurin, when ingested), which is found in VCO, is only available naturally from mother?s milk, nature?s perfect food. These medium chain fatty acids helps to improve nutrient absorption and digestion functions of the body. They also help in regulating blood sugar level and more importantly, protect the body from harmful micro-organisms.

Title: TRESemme Volumizing Mousse Thermal Creations 10022400621828 Boosting Hair Volumizer Mousse(184 g)
Description: It can be challenging to find the right heat-styling product for your hair. TRESemmé Thermal Creations Volume Boosting Mousse actually works with the heat to create sky-high volume. The formula contains unique polymers that leave your hair with flexible fullness that is easy-to-style for a long-lasting effect.Hair Mousse with Volume and HoldTired of limp, dull hair? TRESemmé Thermal Creations Volume Boosting Mousse is the solution to creating full, voluminous looks in four easy steps. Styling with heat can damage hair, but that doesn’t mean you have to shy away from using heat. This volumizing mousse helps provide protection against the heat, while using it to give hair long-lasting, flexible fullness. This heat-styling product is recommended for all hair types, including color-treated, straight and dry hair and for achieving high-volume styles.How to Use TRESemmé Thermal Creations Mousse1. Shake can and dispense 2–3 egg-sized dollops on damp hair (you need more than you think you need). To fully coat, dispense hair mousse directly on a vented brush.2. Then, run the brush from roots to ends to saturate hair.3. For maximum body, blow-dry upside down with a rounded brush, pulling away from the roots and crown (where hair tends to pancake most).4. For added protection from heat styling damage, spray TRESemmé Thermal Creations Heat Tamer Spray before using any heat-styling tools.

Description: royal vitamin A&D ointment jar 1 lb Rensow A&D Ointment is a tattoo industry standard for aftercare treatment. Rensow brand A&D Ointment Applied during tattooing for lubrication.
